    <li>Your boss trying to use slang</li>
    <li>A family group chat getting out of hand</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    The best content comes from real moments, exaggerated slightly for comedy.
  </p>

  <h2 id="ethics">Use it responsibly</h2>
  <p>
    Chat story videos are for entertainment and creative content. The format is so obviously fake (text-on-screen, perfect timing, movie-like pacing) that it reads as fiction instantly. Still: don't use it to impersonate real people, spread misinformation, or fabricate evidence. That can be illegal, not just against platform terms of service.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you're referencing a real person or relationship, make sure it's clearly a joke or fiction. When in doubt, label it as a mockup or skit.
  </p>

